    "Moreover, policymakers can view the results of the surveys using an appropriate dashboard.",
    "Stakeholders (e.g., citizens) can participate to the surveys in order to provide their evaluation feedback about the policies.",
    "ML for public policymaking: From black box to explainable models AI-based policy development relies on ML models that extract policy-related insights from available datasets.",
